operations.
This specification documents only the subset of RBRR variables relevant to
{gcp_service}
operations.

[[rbrr_regime]]
//axvr_regime axf_bash axrd_file_sourced axrd_singleton
{rbrr_regime}::
Repository-wide configuration and installation-wide settings shared across all
{at_recipe_bottle}
operations.

[[rbrr_depot_project_id]]
//axl_voices axrg_variable axvr_kindle axvr_validate axvr_render axtg_project_id
{rbrr_depot_project_id}::
{gcp_service}
{gcp_project_id}
where all
{at_recipe_bottle}
resources are created and managed.

[[rbrr_gcp_region]]
//axl_voices axrg_variable axvr_kindle axvr_validate axvr_render axtg_region
{rbrr_gcp_region}::
Default
{gcp_service}
region for regional services like
{gar_service}
and
{gcb_service}.

[[rbrr_gar_repository]]
//axl_voices axrg_variable axvr_kindle axvr_validate axvr_render axtg_project_id
{rbrr_gar_repository}::
{gar_service}
{rbtgi_repository}
within
{rbrr_depot_project_id}
for
{at_bottle_image_s}
and
{rbtgi_metadata_s}.

[[rbrr_secrets_dir]]
//axl_voices axrg_variable axvr_kindle axvr_validate axvr_render axtu_path
{rbrr_secrets_dir}::
Directory containing service account credential files for all operational roles.
Validated to exist before credential file paths are derived.

[[rbrr_retriever_rbra_file]]
//axl_voices axrd_constructed axtu_path
{rbrr_retriever_rbra_file}::
Path to the
{rbtr_retriever}
{rbtgi_rbra_file}
for container image operations.
Derived from
{rbrr_secrets_dir}
as `retriever/rbra.env`.

[[rbrr_director_rbra_file]]
//axl_voices axrd_constructed axtu_path
{rbrr_director_rbra_file}::
Path to the
{rbtr_director}
{rbtgi_rbra_file}
for build submission and image management.
Derived from
{rbrr_secrets_dir}
as `director/rbra.env`.

[[rbrr_governor_rbra_file]]
//axl_voices axrd_constructed axtu_path
{rbrr_governor_rbra_file}::
Path to the
{rbtr_governor}
{rbtgi_rbra_file}
for
{gcp_project_id}
administration.

